title: "Witch's Specials" Halloween Long Swag
description: "Witch's Specials" Halloween Long Swag 36" long I loved this Halloween menu board sign! I wanted to create a swag with some of the specials in full display. But first I covered the evergreen swag with full deco mesh ribbon poofs & curls, and then added fun Halloween ribbon tails & glittery picks. See if you can spot the ingredients for the specials: Finger Fritters Spider Salad Mice Scream Sundae Monster Munchies (hint: check out the big bow) This would be a fun decor item in your kitchen, at your Halloween party buffet, or even in a restaurant.

title: Woodland Elegance Christmas Wreath
description: Woodland Elegance Christmas Wreath 22" across This beautiful grapevine wreath will look amazing on your front door this year.
